strings.Value: "Elina, could you give me a bottle of wine?"
"Thank you for organizing such a wonderful party for Ekun!"
[Leave] "Well, I'm going to go check in on some of the others!"
"Are you answering your ruler's command with a question?"
"I need a bottle of wine. Now, I'm going to count to three. One..."
"I need a bottle for Ntavi. She's our guest — you can't refuse her food and drinks."
"What can I do for you, Your Grace?"

"My pleasure, Your Grace! I am happy everything turned out this way as well... Besides, entertaining a man such as Ekundayo is a pleasure!" {n}The innkeeper giggles, covering her mouth with a handkerchief.{/n}
"Don't bother with the bottle, Your Grace. I'll pour for you — just bring a glass!"
{n}The innkeeper raises an eyebrow.{/n} "I have no idea why Your Grace invited this harpy... Of course, you know better, but still..."
{n}The innkeeper makes a long face.{/n} "There, there, here you go, Your Grace..."
